<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Zaila'n Awi Hitiu</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Suihlung helin tangtin ka gal thil a,
 Ngomei a kai chii-chiei khaw tang a bawm.

[V2]
 Zailan awi hitiu Lalpen suihlung a hel ni'n,
 Thilhing leh thilhinglo leh a gi hawihteu tawh,
 Gamtin dim hen I kipah nau la gin.

[V3]
 2. Halhin ka chung van khuo ka gal thila,
 Aw nawpna vak zam chiei khun lunglai ei kuoi.

[V4]
 3. Van mi leh kingkang la gi a thangvel,
 Sietlei lungkhamna gam hi a thangvel,

[V5]
 4. Hungun, zaila sai tiu Lalpa ma ah,
 Aw A hehpih lopi zailan awi hitiu.

[V6]
 5. Zai awihpih ka nuom thil chitin chengte,
 Aw, va aw hawihte tawh lei gamthip ahin.</lyrics>
<author>Kamlala</author>
<hymn_number>170</hymn_number>
</song>